題？可以如何調整？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "837435a7f61f", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "305", "s": "1115", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "勞資關係", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-8b44517b-moex-00228', 'locality-8b44517b', 'locality-8b44517b-moex-110-ad750edf', 'sub-locality-8b44517b-02', NULL, 'essay', '新冠肺炎（COVID-19）之蔓延，造成各國人民生命與財產嚴重損失，同
